"""
Parameter Sweep — Rolling Window / Threshold / Stop Loss
=========================================================
Entry/exit based on price vs message DENSITY correlation only.
Sentiment is ignored entirely.

Fixes applied:
  1. No pct_change filter — all trades counted regardless of move size.
  2. One trade per move — after entering, cursor jumps to the exit window
     so the same price move cannot be counted multiple times.

Fixed values when not being swept:
  Correlation threshold : 0.3
  Rolling window        : 400 min
  Trailing stop loss    : 30%

Sweeps:
  threshold     : 0.1 → 1.0  (step 0.1)
  rolling window: 10  → 960  (step 10)
  stop loss     : 5, 10, 15, 20, 25, 30%

Requirements:
    pip install curl_cffi pandas scipy pytz
"""

